<i>verb</i>: 휴양하다 [휴양하다], 요양하다 [요양하다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>휴양하다 [휴양하다]</dt><br>
<dd>rest; get away; relax; recuperate</dd><br>
<dd>편안히 쉬면서 건강을 잘 돌보다.</dd><br>
<dd>To take care of one's health by relaxing.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>요양하다 [요양하다]</dt><br>
<dd>recuperate</dd><br>
<dd>편안히 쉬면서 몸을 보살피고 병을 치료하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To take care of one's body and cure one's illness by relaxing.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>